<p><strong>Paul</strong>—The Jewish apostle to the Gentiles who wrote many epistles and predicted end-time events as recorded in the New Testament.</p>
<p><strong>Peace</strong>—A condition synonymous with salvation, wrought by Jehovah God of Israel, which characterizes the earth&rsquo;s millennial age.</p>
<p><strong>Perdition</strong>—A point of no return for those who descend spiritually by committing gross crimes such as murder, molestation, and satanic rituals.</p>
