<p><strong>Songs of Salvation</strong>—Hymns of praise and thanksgiving by those whom God delivers, notably by his elect who live into the millennial age.</p>
<p><strong>Sons and Daughters of God</strong>—In the Book of Isaiah, a spiritual category of God&rsquo;s elect or those who attain the son/servant level.</p>
<p><strong>Sons and Servants of God</strong>—In the Book of Isaiah, those who serve as proxy saviors to God&rsquo;s people under the terms of the Davidic Covenant</p>
